We aimed to collect diverse {{2111.13611_FO0033||FO}} URLs per entity by issuing a set of search engine queries per entity, e.g., ``about PER'', ``PER biography'', ``ORG history''. A total of {{2111.13611_FO0034||FO}} set of queries for PER and {{2111.13611_FO0035||FO}} for ORG was designed. Since the URLs returned over the set of queries were not always unique, we retained the duplicated URL only once.